---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import IntroTitle from '../components/IntroTitle.astro';
import ProjectList from '../components/ProjectList.astro';
import Showcase from '../components/Showcase.astro';
import ResumeModal from '../components/ResumeModal.astro';
import BlogButton from '../components/BlogButton.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import closingImg from '../assets/closing.png';
import { featured, more } from '../data/projects';
---
<Base>
  <IntroTitle />

  <p class="lede" data-reveal>graphics · engines · infrastructure</p>

  <section class="section col">
    <p class="intro" data-reveal data-speed="0.94">I'm Bahadir — a rising junior CS student who can't really rest until I understand how something actually works. So I build it from scratch, even when that's a ridiculous idea: a Vulkan renderer, a 16-bit CPU, a distributed compute grid. A lot of them started as "there's no way I pull this off," right up until I did.</p>

    <p class="intro" data-reveal data-speed="0.94">A nasty bug can drive me up the wall for hours — then it clicks, and that snap of everything making sense is the best feeling I know. I chase it every day, and it's all pointed at one thing: graphics programming and game dev. That's what I'm building toward.</p>
  </section>

  <Showcase projects={featured} />

  <section class="section col">
    <h2 data-reveal>more</h2>
    <ProjectList projects={more} reveal />

    <p class="hiring" data-reveal>I'm looking for internships and roles in graphics, engines, and game dev — or any hard systems problem where I can go deep and learn fast. If that sounds like your team, I'd love to talk.</p>

    <p data-reveal>Say hi —<br /><a class="live" data-cursor="link" href="https://github.com/jackthepunished" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/jackthepunished</a><br /><a class="live" data-cursor="link" href="mailto:kosapinarbahadir@gmail.com">kosapinarbahadir@gmail.com</a></p>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing statement. As this enters view the vortex fades out (vortex.ts
       reads [data-vortex-fade]) so the glyphs disperse instead of forming a word. -->
  <section class="closing" data-vortex-fade>
    <figure class="closing__plate" data-reveal>
      <Image
        class="closing__img"
        src={closingImg}
        alt="Monochrome engraving — a classical marble bust before a Greek temple, flanked by ornate urns, with open books at its base."
        widths={[680, 1360]}
        sizes="(max-width: 760px) 90vw, 680px"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </figure>
    <p class="closing__quote" data-reveal>until death all defeat is psychological</p>
  </section>

  <BlogButton slot="fixed" />
  <ResumeModal slot="fixed" />
</Base>
